had time for us.

00:28:45.150 --> 00:28:46.610
One of the strongest supporters

00:28:46.610 --> 00:28:49.840
of Burleigh's work was A. Walter
Kramer, the music reviewer

00:28:49.840 --> 00:28:52.710
of the Journal Musical America.

00:28:52.710 --> 00:28:56.110 position:56%
