the Day was in Her Face,

00:35:38.340 --> 00:35:41.080
the last of the Passionale songs.

00:35:41.080 --> 00:35:47.600
In October 1915 Musical America
featured 27 noted concert artists

00:35:47.600 --> 00:35:51.200
who listed their 10
favorite American songs.

00:35:51.200 --> 00:35:56.000 position:56%
Six of these singers listed songs
by Burleigh, of the other 21 singers

00:35:56.000 --> 00:36:00.770
